column1: # Title: Comtrade country code to ISO mapping
# Comments:Nov 25th 2019: Note that as Taiwan is not recognized by the UN there is no TWN ISO specified in the comtrade_ISO mappings. According to COMTRADE code 490 is (in practice) only Taiwan
column2: so it is listed as TWN here rather than NA
column3: but when/if better data is available for Taiwan we may want to update
